_sText:
Hello, I made this sauna map for all sauna lovers and haters. De_CitySauna is good looking Swimming hall sauna map, whitch features two bomb plant areas(two sauna), 3D city skybox and many other things, also high fps(150-250) and fast gameplay. I hope you like it!

If you find a bug, i hope you let me know about it.
